This document defines the Blite language grammar in 
developer to machine form. 

This's a simplified version of the languages, it focus only
service definitions, basic activities and communications primitives.

<deployments> 		::= 
			"{" <service> "}" ("||" "{" <service> "}")*

<service>		::=
			"[" <start_activity> "]"

<activity>		::=
			<basic_activity>
		|
			<sequence_activity>

<basic_activity>	::=
			<empty_activity>
		|
			<exit_activity>
		|
			<invoke_activity>
		|
			<receive_activity>
		|
			<assign_activity>

<sequence_activity>	::=
			"{" (<activity> ";" 
